'''Cosmonova''' is an IMAX venue in [[Swedish Museum of Natural History]], [[Sweden]].<ref name=Statens>{{cite web|title=Naturhistoriska riksmuseet |url=http://www.sfv.se/fastigheter/sverige/stockholms-lan-ab/museer/naturhistoriska-riksmuseet/ |website=www.sfv.se |publisher=Statens Fastinghetsverk |accessdate=17 August 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014000204/http://www.sfv.se/fastigheter/sverige/stockholms-lan-ab/museer/naturhistoriska-riksmuseet/ |archivedate=14 October 2014 |df= }}</ref> The cinema is also the largest planetarium in Sweden.<ref>{{cite web|title=Om Cosmonova|url=http://www.nrm.se/besokmuseet/cosmonova/omcosmonova.5715.html|website=www.nrm.se|publisher=Swedish Museum of Natural History|accessdate=17 August 2014}}</ref>

