'''''The Radiation Belt and Magnetosphere''''' is a [[book]] written by [[Wilmot N. Hess|Wilmot Hess]] in 1968.<ref>{{cite book|author=James A. Van Allen|title=Origins Of Magnetospheric Physics: An Expanded Edition|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gIIUwymo5oQC&pg=PA7|date=1 October 2004|publisher=University of Iowa Press|isbn=978-1-58729-771-7|pages=7–}}</ref> The intention of the book is to [[wikt:amalgamate|amalgamate]] and sift through some 2500 articles, written since 1960, on this topic.

